OL,5, The Criminal Cases Review Commission   
OL,6, (CCRC) has offered an "unreserved      
OL,7, apology" to an innocent man who spent  
OL,8, 17 years in prison.                    
OL,10,FAndrew Malkinson was wrongly convicted 
OL,11,Fof raping a woman in Salford in 2003,  
OL,12,Fbut was exonerated in July 2023 by DNA 
OL,13,Ftesting.                               
OL,15,FCCRC chairwoman Helen Pitcher said she 
OL,16,Fwas "deeply sorry" for "failing" Mr    
OL,17,FMalkinson.                             
